channel.title: 718 Server development
channel.description:
Hello. I'm Cerulean and I'm currently attempting to start a v718 RSPS. It seems that with my lack of experience and skills in Java, I'm a bit lost with some of the server. I'm looking for a developer/coder to help me with most of the Java related aspects of the server. I'm willing to pay, and we can work on the pay as we go along. I'm willing to agree on a fair price depending on your experience and skills, and what you can help me do. You can reply to this post, message me, or add me on skype.
Thank you!
